On your computer, open Chrome.

Click JavaScript.

Turn on Allowed

Here's the issue: video is about ~330MB, and chrome and FF stream the video in one 0- range request, while Safari breaks it up into 64k chunks. Unfortunately, since the WARC records are not seekable, it ends up trying to load the full 330MB each time, eventually crashing the SW
